data.description: Discover the epitome of comfort and charm in this beautiful and cozy 2-bed, 1-bath home that's ready for you to move in and make it your own. The garage has been thoughtfully converted into a versatile rec room, offering extra space for entertaining or potentially serving as a third bedroom to suit your needs.As you step into the heart of the home, you'll find a warm and inviting living space that exudes a welcoming atmosphere. The practical layout maximizes every inch, creating a seamless flow between rooms. The well-appointed kitchen is a delightful space for culinary creations, while the bedrooms offer a retreat at the end of the day.One of the highlights of this property is the expansive backyard, a blank canvas awaiting your creative touch. Whether you envision a relaxing oasis, a vibrant garden, or even a sparkling pool, the possibilities are endless. The corner lot location and cul-de-sac setting add an extra layer of privacy and tranquility to this already appealing residence.Harness the power of the sun with installed solar panels, a thoughtful addition that not only benefits the environment but also trims down your power bills. The cost for the solar panels is approximately $70 per month.Conveniently located near freeways, the Antelope Valley Mall, and a variety of restaurants, this home combines comfort with accessibility. It's not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming property your own and start creating lasting memories in a place you'll be proud to call home.
